DISCLAIMER:

This migration tool modifies system configurations and mounts existing disks.
While every effort has been made to ensure safety, the authors assume no
responsibility for:

- Data loss
- System corruption
- Service disruptions
- Failed migrations
- Any other issues arising from the use of this software

ALWAYS:
- Backup your data before migration
- Create VM snapshots in Proxmox
- Test on non-production systems first
- Review and understand the code before running
- Keep backups of all critical data

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.
